    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1866-05-25T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1866-05-25T00:00:00-05:00" n="463"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d463">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Seward</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Washburn</persName>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 46.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Deparment of State,</hi>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1866-05-25">
                            <hi rend="italic">May</hi> 25, 1866</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir:</hi> I have to acknowledge the receipt of your
                    despatch of March 16th last, giving me an interesting account of your
                    proceedings up to that date, and of your efforts to reach your post of duty.
                    Your perseverance in the endeavor to accomplish the latter object is most
                    commendable and has my approval. I hope that every impediment to your doing so
                    will have disappeared before you receive this reply, and that the war may soon
                    terminate, to the relief of all the parties concerned in it.</p>
                <p>I am, sir, your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>WILLIAM H. SEWARD.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Charles A. Washburn,</hi> Esq., &amp;<hi rend="italic"
                            >c</hi>., &amp;<hi rend="italic">c</hi>., &amp;<hi rend="italic"
                        >c</hi>.</p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
